trans-unit.source: Represents a proxy in a ClickOnce application manifest.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ProxyStub"></xref> class.
Gets the IID of the interface from which the interface described by the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ProxyStub.IID"></xref> property is derived.
The IID of the base interface.
Gets the IID of the interface for which the proxy is being declared.
The IID must have braces ({}) surrounding it.
The IID of the interface.
Gets the name of the component.
The name of the component.
Gets the number of methods in the component.
The number of methods in the component.
Gets the GUID for the type library for the component.
The GUID for the type library.
Gets or sets a property that is used to serialize the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ProxyStub.BaseInterface"></xref> property to an XML file.
The value of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ProxyStub.BaseInterface"></xref> property.
Gets or sets a property that is used to serialize the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ProxyStub.IID"></xref> property to an XML file.
The value of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ProxyStub.IID"></xref> property.
Gets or sets a property that is used to serialize the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ProxyStub.Name"></xref> property to an XML file.
The value of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ProxyStub.Name"></xref> property.
Gets or sets a property that is used to serialize the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ProxyStub.NumMethods"></xref> property to an XML file.
The value of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ProxyStub.NumMethods"></xref> property.
Gets or sets a property that is used to serialize the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ProxyStub.TlbId"></xref> property to an XML file.
The value of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ProxyStub.TlbId"></xref> property.
